                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> und Peters der
                            <expan>Tyntn<ex>er</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für uns besant <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        zu red gesaczt und so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in geredt, daz sie
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> selbs <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewht den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan>
<expan>Melmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> icht zu <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit seinem
                            <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des reich
                                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so die
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim sein on geverd. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vi</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan> Christi.</ab>
